com.yworks.yfiles.graphml

Class XmlName

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yworks.yfiles.graphml.XmlName

  • public class XmlName
extends Object
    Represents an XML name consisting of a local (unqualified) name for an element or attribute and the URI of the namespace for that element or attribute.

      • equals

        public static boolean equals(String name,
                             XmlName xmlName)
        Convenience method that compares a given (unqualified) name to the given XmlName. This method returns true if the local name matches the given string and the given XmlName has no namespace (either null or the empty string).
        Parameters:
        name - The name to match.
        xmlName - The XmlName to match.
        Returns:
        If the given name is equal to the given XmlName.
